# Copy to .env (or export directly) to enable LIVE mode (real LLM calls).
# Without any of these set, the pipeline runs fully offline using
# deterministic heuristics — no key required for a first run.

# Option 1: Groq -- FREE, no credit card, no expiration, generous rate limits.
# Get a key at https://console.groq.com/keys
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# Option 2: Google Gemini -- also free to sign up, but some accounts see the
# free quota gated at 0 until a billing account is linked.
# Get a key at https://aistudio.google.com ("Get API Key").
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...

# Option 3: Anthropic (Claude) -- paid, $5 free trial credit for new accounts.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Option 4: OpenAI -- paid, $5 free trial credit for new accounts.
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
